            "title": "Old Testament Reading",
            "api_nlt_to_ref": "Jeremiah.33:1-34:22",
            "value": "%3Cdiv%20class%3D%22%20NLT%20NLT%20BibleText%20section%22%3E%3Csection%3E%3Ch2%20class%3D%22bk_ch_vs_header%22%3EJeremiah%2033%3A1-34%3A22%2C%20NLT%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22jere_33_1%22%20bk%3D%22jere%22%20ch%3D%2233%22%20vn%3D%221%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22chapter-number%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22cw%22%3EJeremiah%3C%2Fspan%3E%26%23xA0%3B%3Cspan%20class%3D%22cw_ch%22%3E33%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22subhead%22%3EPromises%20of%20Peace%20and%20Prosperity%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22body-ch-hd%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E1%3C%2Fspan%3EWhile%20Jeremiah%20was%20still%20confined%20in%20the%20courtyard%20of%20the%20guard%2C%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%20gave%20him%20this%20second%20message%3A%20%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22jere_33_2%22%20bk%3D%22jere%22%20ch%3D%2233%22%20vn%3D%222%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E2%3C%2Fspan%3E%26%23x201C%3BThis%20is%20what%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%20says%26%23x2014%3Bthe%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%20who%20made%20the%20earth%2C%20who%20formed%20and%20established%20it%2C%20whose%20name%20is%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%3A%20%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22jere_33_3%22%20bk%3D%22jere%22%20ch%3D%2233%22%20vn%3D%223%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E3%3C%2Fspan%3EAsk%20me%20and%20I%20will%20tell%20you%20remarkable%20secrets%20you%20do%20not%20know%20about%20things%20to%20come.%20%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22jere_33_4%22%20bk%3D%22jere%22%20ch%3D%2233%22%20vn%3D%224%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E4%3C%2Fspan%3EFor%20this%20is%20what%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%2C%20the%20God%20of%20Israel%2C%20says%3A%20You%20have%20torn%20down%20the%20houses%20of%20this%20city%20and%20even%20the%20king%26%23x2019%3Bs%20palace%20to%20get%20materials%20to%20strengthen%20the%20walls%20against%20the%20siege%20ramps%20and%20swords%20of%20the%20enemy.%20%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22jere_33_5%22%20bk%3D%22jere%22%20ch%3D%2233%22%20vn%3D%225%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E5%3C%2Fspan%3EYou%20expect%20to%20fight%20the%20Babylonians%2C%3Ca%20class%3D%22a-tn%22%3E*%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn-ref%22%3E33%3A5%3C%2Fspan%3E%20Or%20%3Cem%3EChaldeans.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%20but%20the%20men%20of%20this%20city%20are%20already%20as%20good%20as%20dead%2C%20for%20I%20have%20determined%20to%20destroy%20them%20in%20my%20terrible%20anger.%20I%20have%20abandoned%20them%20because%20of%20all%20their%20wickedness.%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%0A%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22jere_33_6%22%20bk%3D%22jere%22%20ch%3D%2233%22%20vn%3D%226%22%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E6%3C%2Fspan%3E%26%23x201C%3BNevertheless%2C%20the%20time%20will%20come%20when%20I%20will%20heal%20Jerusalem%26%23x2019%3Bs%20wounds%20and%20give%20it%20prosperity%20and%20true%20peace.%20%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22jere_33_7%22%20bk%3D%22jere%22%20ch%3D%2233%22%20vn%3D%227%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E7%3C%2Fspan%3EI%20will%20restore%20the%20fortunes%20of%20Judah%20and%20Israel%20and%20rebuild%20their%20towns.%20%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22jere_33_8%22%20bk%3D%22jere%22%20ch%3D%2233%22%20vn%3D%228%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E8%3C%2Fspan%3EI%20will%20cleanse%20them%20of%20their%20sins%20against%20me%20and%20forgive%20all%20their%20sins%20of%20rebellion.%20%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22jere_33_9%22%20bk%3D%22jere%22%20ch%3D%2233%22%20vn%3D%229%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E9%3C%2Fspan%3EThen%20this%20city%20will%20bring%20me%20joy%2C%20glory%2C%20and%20honor%20before%20all%20the%20nations%20of%20the%20earth!%20The%20people%20of%20the%20world%20will%20see%20all%20the%20good%20I%20do%20for%20my%20people%2C%20and%20they%20will%20tremble%20with%20awe%20at%20the%20peace%20and%20prosperity%20I%20provide%20for%20them.%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%0A%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22jere_33_10%22%20bk%3D%22jere%22%20ch%3D%2233%22%20vn%3D%2210%22%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E10%3C%2Fspan%3E%26%23x201C%3BThis%20is%20what%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%20says%3A%20You%20have%20said%2C%20%26%23x2018%3BThis%20is%20a%20desolate%20land%20where%20people%20and%20animals%20have%20all%20disappeared.%26%23x2019%3B%20Yet%20in%20the%20empty%20streets%20of%20Jerusalem%20and%20Judah%26%23x2019%3Bs%20other%20towns%2C%20there%20will%20be%20heard%20once%20more%20%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22jere_33_11%22%20bk%3D%22jere%22%20ch%3D%2233%22%20vn%3D%2211%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E11%3C%2Fspan%3Ethe%20sounds%20of%20joy%20and%20laughter.%20The%20joyful%20voices%20of%20bridegrooms%20and%20brides%20will%20be%20heard%20again%2C%20along%20with%20the%20joyous%20songs%20of%20people%20bringing%20thanksgiving%20offerings%20to%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E.%20They%20will%20sing%2C%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%0A%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet1-sp%22%3E%26%23x2018%3BGive%20thanks%20to%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%20of%20Heaven%26%23x2019%3Bs%20Armies%2C%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2%22%3Efor%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%20is%20good.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2%22%3EHis%20faithful%20love%20endures%20forever!%26%23x2019%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22body-fl-sp%22%3EFor%20I%20will%20restore%20the%20prosperity%20of%20this%20land%20to%20what%20it%20was%20in%20the%20past%2C%20says%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22jere_33_12%22%20bk%3D%22jere%22%20ch%3D%2233%22%20vn%3D%2212%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E12%3C%2Fspan%3E%26%23x201C%3BThis%20is%20what%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%20of%20Heaven%26%23x2019%3Bs%20Armies%20says%3A%20This%20land%26%23x2014%3Bthough%20it%20is%20now%20desolate%20and%20has%20no%20people%20and%20animals%26%23x2014%3Bwill%20once%20more%20have%20pastures%20where%20shepherds%20can%20lead%20their%20flocks.%20%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22jere_33_13%22%20bk%3D%22jere%22%20ch%3D%2233%22%20vn%3D%2213%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E13%3C%2Fspan%3EOnce%20again%20shepherds%20will%20count%20their%20flocks%20in%20the%20towns%20of%20the%20hill%20country%2C%20the%20foothills%20of%20Judah%2C%3Ca%20class%3D%22a-tn%22%3E*%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn-ref%22%3E33%3A13%3C%2Fspan%3E%20Hebrew%20%3Cem%3Ethe%20Shephelah.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%20the%20Negev%2C%20the%20land%20of%20Benjamin%2C%20the%20vicinity%20of%20Jerusalem%2C%20and%20all%20the%20towns%20of%20Judah.%20I%2C%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%2C%20have%20spoken!%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%0A%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22jere_33_14%22%20bk%3D%22jere%22%20ch%3D%2233%22%20vn%3D%2214%22%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E14%3C%2Fspan%3E%26%23x201C%3BThe%20day%20will%20come%2C%20says%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%2C%20when%20I%20will%20do%20for%20Israel%20and%20Judah%20all%20the%20good%20things%20I%20have%20promised%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22jere_33_15%22%20bk%3D%22jere%22%20ch%3D%2233%22%20vn%3D%2215%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet1-vn-sp%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E15%3C%2Fspan%3E%26%23x201C%3BIn%20those%20days%20and%20at%20that%20time%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2%22%3EI%20will%20raise%20up%20a%20righteous%20descendant%3Ca%20class%3D%22a-tn%22%3E*%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn-ref%22%3E33%3A15%3C%2Fspan%3E%20Hebrew%20%3Cem%3Ea%20righteous%20branch.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%20from%20King%20David%26%23x2019%3Bs%20line.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2%22%3EHe%20will%20do%20what%20is%20just%20and%20right%20throughout%20the%20land.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22jere_33_16%22%20bk%3D%22jere%22%20ch%3D%2233%22%20vn%3D%2216%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet1-vn%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E16%3C%2Fspan%3EIn%20that%20day%20Judah%20will%20be%20saved%2C%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2%22%3Eand%20Jerusalem%20will%20live%20in%20safety.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet1%22%3EAnd%20this%20will%20be%20its%20name%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2%22%3E%26%23x2018%3BThe%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%20Is%20Our%20Righteousness.%26%23x2019%3B%3Ca%20class%3D%22a-tn%22%3E*%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn-ref%22%3E33%3A16%3C%2Fspan%3E%20Hebrew%20%3Cem%3EYahweh%20Tsidqenu.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22jere_33_17%22%20bk%3D%22jere%22%20ch%3D%2233%22%20vn%3D%2217%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22body-fl-sp%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E17%3C%2Fspan%3EFor%20this%20is%20what%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%20says%3A%20David%20will%20have%20a%20descendant%20sitting%20on%20the%20throne%20of%20Israel%20forever.%20%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22jere_33_18%22%20bk%3D%22jere%22%20ch%3D%2233%22%20vn%3D%2218%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E18%3C%2Fspan%3EAnd%20there%20will%20always%20be%20Levitical%20priests%20to%20offer%20burnt%20offerings%20and%20grain%20offerings%20and%20sacrifices%20to%20me.%26%23x201D%3B%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%0A%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22jere_33_19%22%20bk%3D%22jere%22%20ch%3D%2233%22%20vn%3D%2219%22%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E19%3C%2Fspan%3EThen%20this%20message%20came%20to%20Jeremiah%20from%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%3A%20%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22jere_33_20%22%20bk%3D%22jere%22%20ch%3D%2233%22%20vn%3D%2220%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E20%3C%2Fspan%3E%26%23x201C%3BThis%20is%20what%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%20says%3A%20If%20you%20can%20break%20my%20covenant%20with%20the%20day%20and%20the%20night%20so%20that%20one%20does%20not%20follow%20the%20other%2C%20%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22jere_33_21%22%20bk%3D%22jere%22%20ch%3D%2233%22%20vn%3D%2221%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E21%3C%2Fspan%3Eonly%20then%20will%20my%20covenant%20with%20my%20servant%20David%20be%20broken.%20Only%20then%20will%20he%20no%20longer%20have%20a%20descendant%20to%20reign%20on%20his%20throne.%20The%20same%20is%20true%20for%20my%20covenant%20with%20the%20Levitical%20priests%20who%20minister%20before%20me.%20%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22jere_33_22%22%20bk%3D%22jere%22%20ch%3D%2233%22%20vn%3D%2222%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E22%3C%2Fspan%3EAnd%20as%20the%20stars%20of%20the%20sky%20cannot%20be%20counted%20and%20the%20sand%20on%20the%20seashore%20cannot%20be%20measured%2C%20so%20I%20will%20multiply%20the%20descendants%20of%20my%20servant%20David%20and%20the%20Levites%20who%20minister%20before%20me.%26%23x201D%3B%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%0A%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22jere_33_23%22%20bk%3D%22jere%22%20ch%3D%2233%22%20vn%3D%2223%22%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E23%3C%2Fspan%3EThe%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%20gave%20another%20message%20to%20Jeremiah.%20He%20said%2C%20%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22jere_33_24%22%20bk%3D%22jere%22%20ch%3D%2233%22%20vn%3D%2224%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E24%3C%2Fspan%3E%26%23x201C%3BHave%20you%20noticed%20what%20people%20are%20saying%3F%26%23x2014%3B%26%23x2018%3BThe%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%20chose%20Judah%20and%20Israel%20and%20then%20abandoned%20them!%26%23x2019%3B%20They%20are%20sneering%20and%20saying%20that%20Israel%20is%20not%20worthy%20to%20be%20counted%20as%20a%20nation.%20%3